    {
      "text": "So, starting from the front door.",
      "sequenceNumber": 0,
      "startTimeSeconds": 0,
      "endTimeSeconds": 2
    },
    {
      "text": "Airlock is something we always neglect. What are we doing in there?",
      "sequenceNumber": 1,
      "startTimeSeconds": 2,
      "endTimeSeconds": 7
    },
    {
      "text": "What are we doing in the airlock?",
      "sequenceNumber": 2,
      "startTimeSeconds": 7,
      "endTimeSeconds": 9
    },
    {
      "text": "I mean, the challenge is always we need bright lights. We can't do too much. There's not much space.",
      "sequenceNumber": 3,
      "startTimeSeconds": 11,
      "endTimeSeconds": 15
    },
    {
      "text": "So, I haven't thought through too much in the specific airlock.",
      "sequenceNumber": 4,
      "startTimeSeconds": 15,
      "endTimeSeconds": 19
    },
    {
      "text": "But we had...",
      "sequenceNumber": 5,
      "startTimeSeconds": 19,
      "endTimeSeconds": 21
    },
    {
      "text": "But Siobhan's idea here was that when you come in, you play with people's old ideas of voodoo.",
      "sequenceNumber": 6,
      "startTimeSeconds": 21,
      "endTimeSeconds": 27
    },
    {
      "text": "You actually have a voodoo doll.",
      "sequenceNumber": 7,
      "startTimeSeconds": 27,
      "endTimeSeconds": 29
    },
    {
      "text": "And you have the kind of thing where you get people to think about their possible preconceptions.",
      "sequenceNumber": 8,
      "startTimeSeconds": 29,
      "endTimeSeconds": 34
    },
    {
      "text": "And then on the inside, you take away the voodoo doll.",
      "sequenceNumber": 9,
      "startTimeSeconds": 34,
      "endTimeSeconds": 37
    },
    {
      "text": "So, you're moving away from that sort of thing.",
      "sequenceNumber": 10,
      "startTimeSeconds": 37,
      "endTimeSeconds": 40
    },
    {
      "text": "But that would be interesting to play with.",
      "sequenceNumber": 11,
      "startTimeSeconds": 40,
      "endTimeSeconds": 42
    },
    {
      "text": "Tech-wise, it would be nice to have a cyberpunk-y kind of feel.",
      "sequenceNumber": 12,
      "startTimeSeconds": 42,
      "endTimeSeconds": 47
    },
    {
      "text": "How do we make that feel like some weird cyberpunk booth space?",
      "sequenceNumber": 13,
      "startTimeSeconds": 47,
      "endTimeSeconds": 52
    },
    {
      "text": "There might be a mask or something that sits there.",
      "sequenceNumber": 14,
      "startTimeSeconds": 52,
      "endTimeSeconds": 55
    },
    {
      "text": "So, it would be interesting to use one of the backdrops of things.",
      "sequenceNumber": 15,
      "startTimeSeconds": 55,
      "endTimeSeconds": 59
    },
    {
      "text": "That might be interesting.",
      "sequenceNumber": 16,
      "startTimeSeconds": 59,
      "endTimeSeconds": 61
    },
    {
      "text": "But yeah.",
      "sequenceNumber": 17,
      "startTimeSeconds": 61,
      "endTimeSeconds": 62
